I"È<p>Heroku is a container-based cloud Platform as a Service (PaaS). Developers use Heroku to deploy, manage, and scale modern apps. The platform is elegant, flexible, and easy to use, offering developers the simplest path to getting their apps to market.</p>

<p>This tutorial will teach you how to deploy your rails 6 app ot heroku.
The guide assumes that you:</p>
<ul>
  <li>are using linux ubuntu as your OS ()</li>
  <li>are using postgres as your appâ€™s database</li>
  <li>have <a href="https://www.google.com/url?sa=t&amp;rct=j&amp;q=&amp;esrc=s&amp;source=web&amp;cd=&amp;cad=rja&amp;uact=8&amp;ved=2ahUKEwiAttb4ic3tAhWUsnEKHX63D6IQFjAAegQIARAD&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fsignup.heroku.com%2F&amp;usg=AOvVaw2kG63H0ONIjUijpD8T5fVY" target="_blank">opened an account</a> with heroku</li>
</ul>

<p>Lets begin:</p>

